thread.title_full: StorageMart reviewed by Elegant Design Decor

title: Elegant Design Decor
text: My experience was not good at all. I rented a 25*20 unit C71. And the other day it was raining and my storage roof was leaking. And it was around 7 pm and a office was closed. Thanks the next day I reported it. I am not happy at all. I am not satisfied.
